            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <a href="https://comicstore.marvel.com/Captain-Marvel-Vol-2-Civil-War-II/digital-comic/44050?r=1" target="_blank" class="comicbutton comicbutton-accent">Find Out More!</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="~/images/CaptainMarvelcomic3.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">Captain Marvel: Earth's Mightiest Hero Vol. 5</h4>
                <p class="card-text">t’s a bold new frontier for Carol Danvers, soaring to ever greater heights as the leader of the all-new Alpha Flight space program! Yup, Alpha Flight — including classic favorites Puck, Sasquatch and Aurora! </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <a href="https://comicstore.marvel.com/Captain-Marvel-Earths-Mightiest-Hero-Vol-5/digital-comic/50626" target="_blank" class="comicbutton comicbutton-accent">Find Out More!</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="~/images/CaptainMarvelcomic4.jpg" alt="">
