                <h4 class="card-title">Captain Marvel (2016) #3</h4>
                <p class="card-text">Captain Marvel's powers are on the fritz and the timing couldn't be worse. All evidence says that Alpha Flight has a traitor in their midst. How will Carol and her crew figure out the origins of the mystery ship when they can't even trust each other?</p>
